# Bundled CurseForge API key (for personal distribution to friends)
#
# To bake your CurseForge key into the app so friends don't each need their own:
#   1. Copy this file to "cf-key.txt" in the SAME folder (src/main/resources/).
#   2. Put ONLY your key (from console.curseforge.com -> API Keys) in cf-key.txt
#      — just the key, no comments, no extra lines.
#   3. Build the distributable (gradlew run / jpackage) — the key is bundled into the jar.
#
# cf-key.txt is gitignored, so the real key never lands in source control.
# A per-user key set in Settings always overrides the bundled one.
#
# Heads up: a key baked into a downloadable build can be extracted by anyone who has the app.
# Fine for a handful of trusted friends; don't post the build publicly with your key inside.
PASTE-YOUR-CURSEFORGE-KEY-HERE
